The paper deals with signal processing and communication in wireless networks, specifically in multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) interference channels with limited receiver cooperation. This falls under the scope of information theory (cs.IT), networked systems (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer engineering (cs.CE).
